WEBVTT

01:50.000 --> 01:51.729
There are still a few days left.

02:01.920 --> 02:03.080
I forgot my lines.

02:03.680 --> 02:06.600
You didn't forfeit

02:06.720 --> 02:08.180
just to let me win, did you?

02:12.080 --> 02:12.810
Little girl,

02:13.080 --> 02:15.000
are you playing Zixia with him?

02:17.079 --> 02:17.840
No.

02:19.440 --> 02:20.240
Well, yes.

02:20.600 --> 02:22.000
She's shy.

02:23.120 --> 02:25.560
I'll come back in a few days to rent more costumes.

02:25.560 --> 02:26.920
Do you have the costumes for all the characters

02:26.920 --> 02:28.320
in 'A Chinese Odyssey'?

02:28.400 --> 02:28.920
Yes, we do.

02:28.920 --> 02:30.400
Only my shop has them all.

02:30.800 --> 02:32.600
Come with him next time, okay?

02:34.960 --> 02:35.600
Okay.

02:50.280 --> 02:52.880
I didn't expect you to come to a place like this.

02:52.880 --> 02:54.320
We've competed in physics

02:54.320 --> 02:55.320
and basketball.

02:56.360 --> 02:58.800
Today, I want to see how good your billiards is.

02:58.800 --> 03:01.460
You didn't ask me here just to play pool, did you?

03:01.760 --> 03:03.160
What exactly do you want?

03:03.720 --> 03:06.640
Quitting the drama competition doesn't seem like your style.

03:06.640 --> 03:07.560
Can you tell me

03:08.400 --> 03:09.400
why exactly?

03:10.080 --> 03:12.160
I always do things based on my mood.

03:12.680 --> 03:14.080
Is it any of your business?

03:14.080 --> 03:15.280
Why so impatient?

03:15.840 --> 03:17.240
Let's chat while we play.

03:17.520 --> 03:19.579
I have nothing to chat with you about.

03:20.440 --> 03:22.520
You rented Yuanbao's costume, didn't you?

03:22.520 --> 03:24.520
I thought you didn't want her to win.

03:24.680 --> 03:25.840
Why did you help her?

03:30.160 --> 03:31.290
Does it concern you?

03:31.320 --> 03:32.040
Mu Qingjun.

03:32.840 --> 03:34.720
I've never met a rival growing up,

03:35.320 --> 03:36.400
whether in studies

03:37.079 --> 03:38.200
or anything else.

03:38.640 --> 03:40.640
But you are an exception.

03:41.760 --> 03:43.360
You are indeed very capable.

03:43.800 --> 03:46.120
But I hate it most when people yield like it's charity.

03:46.120 --> 03:47.520
You obviously didn't cheat on the physics exam.

03:47.520 --> 03:48.980
Yet you said you copied me.

03:49.640 --> 03:50.920
For this drama festival,

03:50.920 --> 03:53.250
I was planning to compete with you fairly.

03:53.600 --> 03:55.800
I didn't expect you to drop out halfway.

03:55.840 --> 03:56.720
This feeling

03:57.280 --> 03:58.940
makes me very uncomfortable.

03:59.000 --> 03:59.640
Is that so?

04:00.920 --> 04:02.440
Seeing you uncomfortable

04:03.360 --> 04:04.920
makes me feel pretty good.

04:05.600 --> 04:07.840
I know deep down

04:08.000 --> 04:09.860
you want to perform with Yuanbao.

04:10.080 --> 04:10.940
How about this?

04:11.120 --> 04:12.850
Let's have a fair competition.

04:13.080 --> 04:15.480
If you win, you play Joker,

04:16.000 --> 04:17.800
and I'll quit. How about it?

05:08.560 --> 05:10.600
Meng Jingu, you better act well.

05:11.120 --> 05:12.380
Didn't you want to act?

05:13.880 --> 05:15.480
What I want is not important.

05:15.840 --> 05:18.880
What's important is that Yuanbao wants to act with you.

05:18.880 --> 05:20.560
So you better not let her down.

05:21.080 --> 05:22.680
Otherwise I won't spare you.

05:25.200 --> 05:25.840
Also,

05:26.720 --> 05:29.320
Yuanbao really wants to make friends with you.

05:29.560 --> 05:31.320
If you are not sincere,

05:31.960 --> 05:34.880
I will make it impossible for you to stay in Zhicheng.

05:34.880 --> 05:35.920
I mean what I say.

05:47.720 --> 05:48.880
150.

05:49.560 --> 05:50.880
170.

05:53.960 --> 05:55.520
170.

05:56.960 --> 05:58.000
170.

05:58.000 --> 05:58.800
200.

05:59.120 --> 06:00.880
203.

06:02.120 --> 06:03.840
Why is it so little?

06:11.480 --> 06:14.320
Actually, as long as Mutou is here,

06:14.600 --> 06:16.560
I feel at ease for some reason.

06:17.120 --> 06:19.050
When we performed in class before,

06:19.080 --> 06:20.810
it was always just the two of us.

06:20.840 --> 06:23.640
Leaving him behind and choosing Meng Jingu this time,

06:23.640 --> 06:25.280
he must be feeling upset.

06:25.560 --> 06:28.480
No, Mutou has been sensitive since childhood.

06:28.720 --> 06:31.580
I still need to save up for a nice gift to cheer him up.

06:36.920 --> 06:38.250
Little pig, little pig.

06:38.400 --> 06:40.360
You have to grow up fast.

06:43.960 --> 06:46.840
Brother Mutou, thank you for renting the clothes.

06:47.080 --> 06:48.720
Please allow me to treat you

06:48.720 --> 06:51.520
to ice cream another day as a token of my gratitude.

06:59.720 --> 07:00.760
I want two.

07:19.400 --> 07:22.260
All three are fine. Just don't get an upset stomach.

07:28.880 --> 07:31.340
Yuanbao really wants to be friends with you.

07:36.560 --> 07:37.920
I'm going to study now.

07:38.000 --> 07:39.840
Come on, Yuanbao.

07:59.360 --> 08:00.040
Yuanbao.

08:02.120 --> 08:04.050
You're actually quite excellent.

08:05.640 --> 08:06.680
What?

08:07.000 --> 08:07.880
Nothing.

08:08.480 --> 08:09.610
I just wanted to say,

08:09.760 --> 08:12.080
don't forget to rehearse after school.

08:12.400 --> 08:14.440
The competition is coming up. We need to hurry.

08:14.440 --> 08:15.200
Don't worry.

08:15.280 --> 08:18.080
I've memorized it thoroughly these past few days.

08:24.320 --> 08:26.400
Aren't you Zhizunbao and Zixia?

08:26.680 --> 08:28.520
Who are you picking clothes for today?

08:28.520 --> 08:30.440
Well, I'm not acting anymore.

08:30.720 --> 08:32.640
I brought my classmates to pick out some clothes.

08:32.640 --> 08:34.640
All right. What clothes do you need?

08:35.000 --> 08:37.600
We also need costumes for the other characters.

08:37.600 --> 08:38.760
The clothes are upstairs.

08:38.760 --> 08:40.400
Let them all come in, okay?

08:40.840 --> 08:41.559
Come.

08:42.200 --> 08:44.860
They're all on the second floor. Take your pick.

08:50.360 --> 08:51.290
This one is good.

08:51.520 --> 08:53.180
There's a Zhu Bajie mask here.

08:55.160 --> 08:56.440
So many clothes!

08:57.920 --> 08:59.120
So annoying.

09:01.040 --> 09:02.000
What is this?

09:03.280 --> 09:05.680
You didn't keep your pig in its pen, did you?

09:07.840 --> 09:08.480
Ruirui.

09:11.480 --> 09:13.520
This is Princess Iron Fan.

09:13.680 --> 09:14.840
Qingyun.

09:15.080 --> 09:16.320
Look, Zhu Bajie's mask.

09:16.320 --> 09:18.360
Didn't you say you didn't like Zhu Bajie yesterday?

09:18.360 --> 09:19.960
Why are you so excited today?

09:20.840 --> 09:21.770
I like him today.

09:21.920 --> 09:22.520
Look,

09:22.560 --> 09:24.560
here are the Fifth Prince's clothes.

09:24.560 --> 09:25.520
My Guanyin.

09:25.920 --> 09:26.800
How is it?

09:26.920 --> 09:28.440
Can I act in a Qing Dynasty drama

09:28.440 --> 09:30.240
if I wear this?

09:30.640 --> 09:32.900
Then you'll have to shave your head bald.

09:32.920 --> 09:33.760
Get lost.

09:36.360 --> 09:38.280
Did I eat too much today?

09:38.720 --> 09:39.960
I hope it fits.

09:40.440 --> 09:42.680
It'll fit. I'm looking forward to it.

09:45.640 --> 09:47.360
Ruirui, let's go.

09:47.760 --> 09:48.320
Go.

09:49.800 --> 09:51.200
Selling pigs.

09:51.240 --> 09:53.200
Cheap.

09:53.520 --> 09:54.280
Your pig

09:54.320 --> 09:56.080
looks like it's pregnant with seven piglets.

09:56.080 --> 09:58.040
Guaranteed profit.

09:59.160 --> 09:59.920
Sloppy pig.

10:12.240 --> 10:13.640
Does it look good, Mutou?

10:15.600 --> 10:16.660
It's quite pretty.

10:33.440 --> 10:34.100
Looks good.

10:34.800 --> 10:36.330
Yours looks quite good too.

10:36.640 --> 10:37.360
Thank you.

10:48.280 --> 10:50.840
Try harder next time. You are still Zhi Zun Bao.

10:50.840 --> 10:51.560
Come on.

10:58.480 --> 11:01.540
Yaqi, you'd definitely look much better in it than her.

11:01.800 --> 11:02.440
No.

11:02.520 --> 11:04.650
I think Yuanbao looks quite good in it.

11:05.920 --> 11:07.250
What's so good about it?

11:08.760 --> 11:09.600
Yuanbao.

11:09.880 --> 11:11.810
You finally look like a girl today.

11:12.880 --> 11:13.560
You...

11:15.320 --> 11:16.360
Well...

11:16.560 --> 11:17.960
Let's take a costume photo together.

11:17.960 --> 11:18.760
Okay.

11:18.960 --> 11:19.920
Come on.

11:20.440 --> 11:21.080
Let's go.

11:22.120 --> 11:22.840
Come on.

11:24.680 --> 11:25.480
Wait a minute.

11:27.120 --> 11:28.160
What are you doing?

11:28.160 --> 11:29.960
Come, let's take a photo together.

11:29.960 --> 11:30.800
Come on.

11:32.000 --> 11:33.860
Come, I'll count three, two, one.

11:33.880 --> 11:34.800
Let's take a picture together.

11:34.800 --> 11:35.960
Say cheese.

11:36.160 --> 11:40.400
Three, two, one, cheese!

11:44.400 --> 11:44.880
All right.

11:44.880 --> 11:45.680
All right, all right.

11:45.680 --> 11:46.480
Got it, got it.

11:46.560 --> 11:48.280
Everyone, please make sure to put away your costumes

11:48.280 --> 11:49.880
and props carefully.

11:50.000 --> 11:50.880
When we get to the school,

11:50.880 --> 11:53.340
they will be managed by Qiao Yan and Qingyun.

12:39.120 --> 12:39.760
Stand up.

12:41.080 --> 12:43.760
Hello, teacher.

12:43.960 --> 12:45.890
Hello, students. Please sit down.

12:46.560 --> 12:47.690
We have a new student

12:47.880 --> 12:49.480
transferring to our class today.

12:49.480 --> 12:51.080
Get along well with each other.

12:51.080 --> 12:52.000
Such a big event,

12:52.000 --> 12:53.440
and I didn't hear a word about it.

12:53.440 --> 12:54.440
That makes no sense.

12:54.440 --> 12:55.560
Yeah, really.

12:55.920 --> 12:56.680
Come in.

13:21.360 --> 13:23.120
She is so pretty!

13:24.160 --> 13:25.480
Please introduce yourself.

13:25.480 --> 13:27.520
Hello everyone, my name is Gu Xinrui.

13:27.520 --> 13:29.120
Please take care of me.

13:30.560 --> 13:32.960
Come on, let's give her a round of applause.

13:33.480 --> 13:34.280
Welcome.

13:35.600 --> 13:37.720
Xinrui, go to the last row

13:37.960 --> 13:39.360
and sit with Mu Qingjun.

13:42.320 --> 13:43.000
Okay.

13:43.360 --> 13:44.200
Mu Qingjun.

13:44.720 --> 13:46.000
Don't distract the new student in class.

13:46.000 --> 13:46.720
Got it.

13:54.040 --> 13:55.040
So beautiful.

13:58.680 --> 13:59.440
Hello.

13:59.520 --> 14:00.450
World Military.

14:05.320 --> 14:06.160
All right.

14:06.200 --> 14:08.460
Everyone, open yesterday's exam paper.

14:08.880 --> 14:10.840
You have 20 minutes to do it.

14:11.120 --> 14:12.320
Then we'll go over it.

14:12.920 --> 14:14.520
Where did this girl transfer from?

14:14.520 --> 14:15.840
She is so pretty.

14:16.400 --> 14:17.640
Don't you think

14:17.720 --> 14:20.560
she outshines Xing Yaqi?

14:21.320 --> 14:22.280
Pretty much.

14:22.560 --> 14:23.680
What are you talking about?

14:23.680 --> 14:25.280
She's a typical rich beauty.

14:26.320 --> 14:27.320
Shang Ningyu.

14:28.120 --> 14:29.380
You know this goddess?

14:29.480 --> 14:30.920
We were middle school classmates.

14:30.920 --> 14:32.320
She was the school belle.

14:32.840 --> 14:33.700
Who is talking?

14:38.080 --> 14:40.480
Goodbye, teacher.

14:40.680 --> 14:41.640
Goodbye, class.

14:42.840 --> 14:44.640
Xinrui, why are you here?

14:44.880 --> 14:45.810
You are here too?

14:45.880 --> 14:46.520
Did you just transfer here?

14:46.520 --> 14:47.650
You know each other?

14:48.640 --> 14:49.800
Middle school classmates.

14:49.800 --> 14:52.400
Weren't you in some... some...

14:52.480 --> 14:52.920
The UK?

14:53.080 --> 14:53.960
Yes, yes, yes.

14:54.800 --> 14:56.360
Yes, I just came back a few days ago.

14:56.360 --> 14:57.160
That's great.

14:58.200 --> 14:59.720
I'm just still not quite used to it.

14:59.720 --> 15:00.920
Come outside with me.

15:02.200 --> 15:02.840
Okay.

15:05.120 --> 15:06.640
Why did he ask her to go outside?

15:06.640 --> 15:08.500
They seem to know each other well.

15:08.840 --> 15:10.600
She went right out when he called.

15:10.600 --> 15:11.800
Hurry, hurry, hurry.

15:12.360 --> 15:13.620
What? What's going on?

15:17.520 --> 15:18.160
Yuanbao.

15:21.640 --> 15:23.400
I've been looking for you for a while.

15:23.400 --> 15:24.920
Why did you come here alone?

15:24.920 --> 15:26.380
Why didn't you wait for me?

15:28.040 --> 15:30.480
I didn't want to interrupt your chat with the new classmate.

15:30.480 --> 15:32.000
So I just...

15:32.120 --> 15:32.840
Xinrui.

15:33.760 --> 15:35.890
She's actually not just my classmate,

15:36.440 --> 15:37.520
but also my sister.

15:38.640 --> 15:39.400
Your sister?

15:40.360 --> 15:43.080
Our relationship is just like yours and Qingyun's.

15:43.080 --> 15:44.920
We grew up together like siblings.

15:44.920 --> 15:46.250
She went abroad before.

15:46.480 --> 15:49.800
But now she suddenly came back because of a back injury.

15:49.920 --> 15:50.960
She didn't even tell me.

15:50.960 --> 15:52.420
I was quite surprised too.

15:54.640 --> 15:55.900
Don't misunderstand.

15:56.760 --> 15:58.160
It's fine. That's good.

16:06.960 --> 16:07.600
What's wrong, bro?

16:07.600 --> 16:09.280
Did I do something wrong?

16:09.360 --> 16:10.000
No.

16:10.480 --> 16:11.610
Let me buy you a cola.

16:11.680 --> 16:12.920
Okay, thank you.

16:23.000 --> 16:24.530
What happened at the cinema

16:24.600 --> 16:26.240
that day?

16:26.920 --> 16:28.360
Did I misunderstand?

16:28.800 --> 16:29.800
Could it be

16:30.480 --> 16:33.280
that she didn't give me the movie ticket secretly?

16:33.520 --> 16:34.680
Should I ask her?

16:35.640 --> 16:36.640
If I ask,

16:37.760 --> 16:38.890
it might be awkward.

16:45.320 --> 16:46.240
Mr. Liu.

16:55.840 --> 16:58.320
Why does he have that movie ticket?

16:59.040 --> 17:00.160
Should I ask him?

17:02.000 --> 17:02.800
Forget it.

17:03.160 --> 17:05.220
I'll just pretend nothing happened.

17:06.839 --> 17:07.880
Um.

17:08.960 --> 17:10.680
Um, you go first.

17:11.640 --> 17:13.040
I'm fine, you go first.

17:13.960 --> 17:15.680
Um, I just wanted to say

17:16.200 --> 17:17.730
that our students recently

17:17.920 --> 17:19.520
have been very motivated

17:19.800 --> 17:20.930
to learn chemistry.

17:20.960 --> 17:22.319
This is all to your credit.

17:22.319 --> 17:22.960
No.

17:23.280 --> 17:25.599
It's because you are a good homeroom teacher.

17:25.599 --> 17:26.240
No.

17:26.319 --> 17:27.650
I can't take the credit.

17:27.720 --> 17:28.920
They really like you.

17:28.960 --> 17:30.600
They only like me because they like you.

17:30.600 --> 17:32.360
No, they like you.

17:32.440 --> 17:33.160
They like you.

17:33.160 --> 17:35.440
They like you.

17:38.440 --> 17:40.680
I have something else to do.

17:40.720 --> 17:42.040
I'll get going now.

17:42.440 --> 17:43.160
Um...

17:43.920 --> 17:44.920
Mr. Xu.

17:49.360 --> 17:50.080
Mr. Tian.

17:50.840 --> 17:53.040
Mu Qingyun, why didn't you knock again?

17:53.640 --> 17:54.320
Alright.

17:55.000 --> 17:55.800
What is it?

17:57.880 --> 17:59.280
I want to play Zhi Zunbao.

17:59.280 --> 18:01.160
Mu Qingyun, the performance is starting soon.

18:01.160 --> 18:02.680
Can you stop making trouble?

18:02.680 --> 18:03.880
I'm not making trouble.

18:03.880 --> 18:05.280
How is this not making trouble?

18:05.280 --> 18:06.280
You perform when you want to,

18:06.280 --> 18:07.680
and quit when you want to.

18:07.880 --> 18:09.320
Do you think your family owns this school?

18:09.320 --> 18:11.280
You think you can do whatever you want?

18:11.280 --> 18:12.040
Mu Qingyun.

18:12.680 --> 18:14.080
A real man

18:14.320 --> 18:16.040
always keeps his word.

18:16.320 --> 18:18.880
You have to be responsible for your own decisions and words.

18:18.880 --> 18:19.720
Exactly.

18:23.040 --> 18:23.960
This.

18:26.520 --> 18:27.850
You are messing around.

18:30.720 --> 18:31.320
Mr. Tian,

18:31.680 --> 18:34.120
I think it's a good thing for students to be proactive.

18:34.120 --> 18:35.120
Don't be angry.

18:35.200 --> 18:36.040
Look at this child,

18:36.040 --> 18:37.720
if they put this cleverness into their studies,

18:37.720 --> 18:39.200
their grades would have improved long ago.

18:39.200 --> 18:40.560
Well, I'll talk to

18:40.640 --> 18:41.920
the class monitors again.

18:41.920 --> 18:43.120
Go back.

18:43.520 --> 18:44.160
Okay.

18:46.160 --> 18:47.760
Yuanbao, this time

18:47.840 --> 18:49.920
you're the highly anticipated female lead.

18:49.920 --> 18:51.520
Because of your hard work,

18:51.640 --> 18:53.080
I am truly happy for you.

18:55.120 --> 18:57.560
But I'm naturally bad at art.

18:57.760 --> 19:00.040
However, I believe what my grandmother said.

19:00.040 --> 19:01.280
Man can conquer nature.

19:01.280 --> 19:03.480
We can rely on our hard work acquired

19:03.600 --> 19:04.840
to change our destiny.

19:04.840 --> 19:05.880
Let's work hard together.

19:05.880 --> 19:06.560
Okay.

19:06.960 --> 19:07.760
Cheer up!

19:07.960 --> 19:08.760
Cheer up!

19:08.800 --> 19:10.200
Hello, Yuanbao. Hello, Ruirui.

19:10.200 --> 19:11.720
Let's have a drink together.

19:11.720 --> 19:13.480
Thank you.

19:13.640 --> 19:14.570
You're welcome.

19:14.720 --> 19:17.250
I heard you're going to act in a play together.

19:17.320 --> 19:18.640
That's great.

19:18.960 --> 19:21.090
Looking forward to your performance.

19:22.480 --> 19:23.340
I just got here.

19:23.400 --> 19:25.680
I'm not familiar with many people yet.

19:25.880 --> 19:27.600
I heard from Jingu that you are sincere

19:27.600 --> 19:28.920
and loyal to your friends.

19:28.920 --> 19:29.640
So,

19:29.720 --> 19:31.580
I hope to be good friends with you.

19:32.400 --> 19:33.000
It's fine.

19:33.160 --> 19:34.160
My desk mate's good friend

19:34.160 --> 19:35.440
is my good friend.

19:35.720 --> 19:36.280
Really?

19:36.480 --> 19:37.200
That's great.

19:37.200 --> 19:38.840
From now on, we are good friends.

19:38.840 --> 19:39.360
Okay,

19:39.480 --> 19:40.320
no problem.

19:41.960 --> 19:44.290
It seems you don't have to take PE classes.

19:45.600 --> 19:48.260
I used to be an art student and practice dancing.

19:48.440 --> 19:49.920
But after a year abroad,

19:50.600 --> 19:51.660
I injured my waist.

19:52.120 --> 19:52.920
In the future,

19:53.320 --> 19:55.980
I might not be able to practice dancing anymore.

19:56.480 --> 19:57.320
Don't be discouraged.

19:57.320 --> 19:58.680
We will all support you.

19:59.160 --> 20:01.480
I still want to learn dancing with you then.

20:01.480 --> 20:02.240
Okay,

20:02.440 --> 20:04.560
then I can teach you.

20:04.720 --> 20:05.080
Okay.

20:05.080 --> 20:06.840
Okay, you can teach us then.

20:07.280 --> 20:09.440
I want to see how you dance that Xinjiang dance.

20:09.440 --> 20:10.080
Together.

20:16.480 --> 20:17.280
Qiao Yan.

20:18.440 --> 20:19.970
What's wrong with your arm?

20:20.200 --> 20:20.640
Nothing.

20:20.640 --> 20:21.720
Are you injured?

20:22.000 --> 20:23.730
Yes, I accidentally bumped it.

20:25.040 --> 20:26.400
I always see you

20:26.400 --> 20:27.760
covered in bruises.

20:28.160 --> 20:29.000
Are you okay?

20:29.200 --> 20:30.400
I'm fine.

20:30.920 --> 20:32.850
I'll be more careful in the future.

20:33.080 --> 20:33.760
But Yaqi,

20:34.000 --> 20:35.440
look at Xiong Yuanbao.

20:36.520 --> 20:39.200
Although she has poor grades and is unreliable,

20:39.760 --> 20:41.560
Mu Qingyun and Meng Jingu

20:42.240 --> 20:43.640
are both very nice to her.

20:44.000 --> 20:45.080
Don't say that.

20:45.400 --> 20:46.320
She and Qingyun

20:46.360 --> 20:47.520
grew up together.

20:47.640 --> 20:49.440
Meng Jingu is also her desk mate,

20:49.640 --> 20:51.920
so it's normal for them to have a good relationship.

20:51.920 --> 20:53.050
Don't overthink it.

20:53.560 --> 20:55.040
Then why do I feel

20:55.320 --> 20:57.560
the way you look at Mu Qingyun recently

20:57.720 --> 20:58.980
is a little different?

21:00.360 --> 21:01.200
No.

21:01.600 --> 21:02.400
No?

21:02.560 --> 21:04.020
Then why are you blushing?

21:05.040 --> 21:06.160
I'm not blushing.

21:07.360 --> 21:08.490
By the way, Qiao Yan.

21:08.560 --> 21:10.560
Why didn't you act in 'A Chinese Odyssey'?

21:10.560 --> 21:12.400
You served everyone the whole time.

21:12.400 --> 21:13.530
That's not like you.

21:14.640 --> 21:16.960
I just feel it would interfere with my studies.

21:16.960 --> 21:18.200
Besides, my dad doesn't like

21:18.200 --> 21:21.400
me participating in activities unrelated to my studies.

21:21.880 --> 21:23.010
All right, go ahead.

21:23.080 --> 21:24.440
Class is about to end. Let's go gather.

21:24.440 --> 21:25.040
Let's go.

21:33.360 --> 21:35.600
Brother, if you really have something on your mind,

21:35.600 --> 21:37.240
why don't you tell me about it?

21:37.240 --> 21:39.040
Maybe I can give you some advice.

21:40.400 --> 21:41.930
I want to strangle someone.

21:42.680 --> 21:43.640
My dear brother!

21:43.800 --> 21:45.160
Take my advice.

21:45.560 --> 21:47.800
There are plenty of fish in the sea.

21:48.000 --> 21:49.930
Why do you keep thinking about her?

21:50.320 --> 21:52.320
Maybe she just sees you as a brother.

21:52.320 --> 21:53.760
Are you overthinking it?

21:56.240 --> 21:58.040
What was the last thing you said?

21:58.240 --> 21:59.040
I said,

21:59.360 --> 22:01.080
she just sees you as a brother.

22:01.440 --> 22:03.880
Are you overthinking it?

22:04.120 --> 22:05.780
Yes, yes, yes. That's the one.

22:10.760 --> 22:12.160
Traveling through time,

22:12.640 --> 22:14.320
we seem to see

22:14.600 --> 22:17.640
that young wet nurse in Jiaodong.

22:18.160 --> 22:19.680
Close at hand,

22:20.120 --> 22:21.720
we deeply feel

22:21.760 --> 22:24.920
the burning heat of a mother's chest.

22:25.200 --> 22:26.560
At Jiaodong Nursery,

22:26.840 --> 22:28.880
there is my childhood wet nurse.

22:29.160 --> 22:31.000
More than 300 women from Rushan.

22:31.120 --> 22:33.980
I'm afraid I won't be able to see without my glasses.

22:34.240 --> 22:37.160
I, Old Bull, will do it.

22:37.440 --> 22:39.320
Why can't I remember the lines?

22:40.720 --> 22:41.520
Back then.

22:42.000 --> 22:43.440
Help me tie this, Yuanbao.

22:43.440 --> 22:44.080
Sure.

22:44.160 --> 22:44.880
Let me see.

22:45.240 --> 22:47.280
There is a strap here in the back.

22:47.360 --> 22:48.690
You can make it tighter.

22:49.960 --> 22:50.440
All right.

22:50.440 --> 22:51.120
Like this.

22:52.000 --> 22:52.860
Is it too tight?

22:54.120 --> 22:55.650
I'll loosen it a bit for you.

22:57.840 --> 22:59.200
I'm holding my breath.

22:59.480 --> 23:01.000
Tong Ruirui, suck your stomach in.

23:01.000 --> 23:02.000
Who to choose?

23:02.240 --> 23:03.240
Who to choose?

23:03.520 --> 23:03.960
Is this okay?

23:03.960 --> 23:06.220
She has always just seen you as a brother.

23:06.280 --> 23:08.000
Are you overthinking it?

23:08.880 --> 23:10.120
I'll redo it for you.

23:10.120 --> 23:12.040
The next group is Class 20, Grade 1.

23:12.040 --> 23:14.100
Please get ready for your rehearsal.

23:20.200 --> 23:20.920
How is it?

23:21.880 --> 23:22.680
What's wrong?

23:23.360 --> 23:24.560
It's almost our class's turn.

23:24.560 --> 23:26.220
But Meng Jingu isn't here yet.

23:26.360 --> 23:27.520
What should we do?

23:27.960 --> 23:28.920
Call him again.

23:37.320 --> 23:38.360
He's not answering.

23:38.360 --> 23:40.890
Could something have happened to Meng Jingu?

23:41.360 --> 23:42.360
I don't think so.

23:43.160 --> 23:44.600
Did you tell Mr. Tian?

23:45.240 --> 23:47.520
Mr. Tian is in a meeting and can't be reached.

23:47.520 --> 23:49.000
Could he have given up?

23:49.120 --> 23:50.040
No.

23:52.080 --> 23:54.120
Meng Jingu isn't that kind of person.

23:54.120 --> 23:55.880
Why don't we talk to the host

23:56.040 --> 23:57.080
and ask them to push

23:57.080 --> 23:58.480
our rehearsal slot back?

23:59.160 --> 24:00.490
We have no other choice.

24:01.080 --> 24:02.210
I'll go talk to them.

24:10.760 --> 24:12.040
Hello, excuse me.

24:12.200 --> 24:14.260
We are missing a student in our class.

24:14.280 --> 24:16.400
How about this? You guys rehearse first.

24:16.400 --> 24:17.000
All right.

24:20.280 --> 24:22.540
They should be here in about ten minutes.

24:25.120 --> 24:25.640
Gulai,

24:25.640 --> 24:26.480
Jin Gulai.

24:26.760 --> 24:29.090
Pour tea for your Uncle Qin and Sister Qin.

24:29.320 --> 24:31.160
Your Sister Qin took time out

24:31.200 --> 24:33.480
of her busy schedule to bring you study notes.

24:33.480 --> 24:35.740
Sharing learning experiences with you.

24:35.760 --> 24:37.290
That is really a rare thing.

24:38.600 --> 24:40.060
Thanks for your hard work.

24:41.440 --> 24:42.720
Give me my phone back.

24:42.920 --> 24:43.800
I really...

24:44.760 --> 24:45.800
Come, have some tea.

24:45.800 --> 24:46.440
Okay.

24:46.480 --> 24:47.280
Have some tea.

24:48.320 --> 24:50.600
Uncle, Jingu really has something to do today.

24:50.600 --> 24:51.600
How about...

24:55.680 --> 24:56.480
I'm sorry.

24:56.880 --> 24:58.080
Mr. Qin, Ms. Qin,

24:58.280 --> 25:00.280
I have something really important today.

25:00.280 --> 25:01.340
I must go right now.

25:01.560 --> 25:03.440
Please excuse me.

25:04.200 --> 25:05.200
Stop right there.

25:06.080 --> 25:07.540
Is some silly performance

25:07.800 --> 25:10.330
more important than your future and studies?

25:13.160 --> 25:15.320
You have already rescheduled the rehearsal four times.

25:15.320 --> 25:17.250
Now we've put you in the last group.

25:17.280 --> 25:18.760
Is your teammate still not here?

25:18.760 --> 25:20.880
He'll be here soon.

25:21.080 --> 25:22.680
Please wait a little longer.

25:24.120 --> 25:26.000
We really don't have that much time.

25:26.000 --> 25:27.800
Besides, we have to clean up.

25:28.280 --> 25:30.200
The competition will officially start tonight.

25:30.200 --> 25:32.000
We can wait for ten more minutes at most.

25:32.000 --> 25:33.120
If he still doesn't show up,

25:33.120 --> 25:34.880
you will have to miss the rehearsal.

25:34.880 --> 25:37.120
Whether you can perform depends on the teacher.

25:37.120 --> 25:39.520
Meng Jingu shouldn't be so unreliable.

25:39.960 --> 25:41.240
Why isn't he here yet?

25:41.440 --> 25:42.880
I did some reckoning,

25:43.080 --> 25:44.080
this matter

25:44.320 --> 25:45.280
is very ominous.

25:46.920 --> 25:48.250
Shut your jinxed mouth.

25:49.760 --> 25:51.360
Is Meng Jingu still not here?

25:52.360 --> 25:54.840
Meng Jingu standing us up without a word

25:54.880 --> 25:56.560
is not his style.

25:57.000 --> 25:58.080
What's going on?

25:58.480 --> 26:00.800
The rehearsal is to coordinate with the lights and music.

26:00.800 --> 26:02.000
Since he is not here,

26:02.800 --> 26:05.040
how about this? You guys go on stage first,

26:05.040 --> 26:06.560
and leave his lines empty.

26:06.720 --> 26:08.520
We can't miss this opportunity.

26:09.920 --> 26:11.800
But Yuanbao and Meng Jingu

26:11.800 --> 26:13.240
have so many scenes together.

26:13.240 --> 26:14.480
If Meng Jingu doesn't come,

26:14.480 --> 26:15.720
we can't let Yuanbao

26:15.760 --> 26:17.090
put on a one-woman show.

26:17.360 --> 26:18.800
Right, Yuanbao can't

26:18.840 --> 26:20.400
just act into thin air.

26:20.480 --> 26:22.080
No one is here to read lines with her.

26:22.080 --> 26:25.140
She won't even know if she's acting too fast or too slow.

26:28.360 --> 26:30.200
Let's not wait anymore. Let's rehearse.

26:30.200 --> 26:31.360
We can't miss this opportunity

26:31.360 --> 26:32.440
because of him.

26:33.240 --> 26:34.840
I will try my best to act well.

26:35.160 --> 26:36.360
Let's all do our best.

26:36.880 --> 26:37.810
I'll try my best.

26:38.800 --> 26:40.600
Let's go.

26:40.680 --> 26:41.240
Let's go.

26:41.680 --> 26:42.680
Come on, Yuanbao.

26:46.080 --> 26:48.480
What are you doing? Are you trying to rebel?

26:48.640 --> 26:50.280
Dad, I'm really going to be late.

26:50.280 --> 26:52.040
I'm begging you, let me go.

26:52.600 --> 26:54.260
I wanted you to study finance,

26:54.560 --> 26:56.960
but you stubbornly insisted on studying physics.

26:56.960 --> 26:58.600
Fine, I let you have your way.

26:59.080 --> 27:00.280
I let you have your way because

27:00.280 --> 27:02.120
you actually had some ideas of your own.

27:02.120 --> 27:03.280
But now I realize

27:03.560 --> 27:05.220
that I've really spoiled you.

27:05.680 --> 27:08.280
You can't even get your priorities straight.

27:08.480 --> 27:09.920
Instead of studying,

27:10.200 --> 27:12.200
you hang out with those poor students all day,

27:12.200 --> 27:13.680
doing useless things.

27:14.560 --> 27:15.360
Today, you made me

27:15.360 --> 27:17.160
lose face in front of outsiders.

27:17.960 --> 27:19.960
You don't even have any manners.

27:20.080 --> 27:21.520
You're going too far.

27:23.000 --> 27:25.720
Jingu, your dad has a bad heart.

27:25.840 --> 27:27.480
He's just doing this for your own good.

27:27.480 --> 27:29.440
Uncle Qin and Sister Qin came today.

27:29.440 --> 27:31.370
How could you just leave like that?

27:32.640 --> 27:33.920
I am not your puppet.

27:35.240 --> 27:36.500
I have my own thoughts.

27:36.800 --> 27:38.460
I have my own life and friends.

27:38.680 --> 27:40.240
Can you please respect me?

27:40.760 --> 27:42.480
We don't respect you?

27:42.800 --> 27:45.200
I think you don't realize how lucky you are.

27:45.280 --> 27:47.240
You will stay in your room today.

27:47.560 --> 27:48.880
When you figure things out,

27:48.880 --> 27:50.080
then you can come out.

27:59.320 --> 28:01.680
Xinrui, please talk some sense into Jingu.

28:01.680 --> 28:04.000
He won't listen to us right now.

28:13.960 --> 28:14.800
Jingu.

28:15.600 --> 28:18.080
No matter what, Uncle Meng has his reasons.

28:18.560 --> 28:20.820
They must be doing this for your own good.

28:21.040 --> 28:22.700
That's what he thinks is good.

28:23.800 --> 28:26.360
The root of the problem is that he is too dictatorial.

28:26.360 --> 28:28.360
But even if you rush there now,

28:28.400 --> 28:29.800
I'm afraid it's too late.

28:30.400 --> 28:31.280
How about

28:31.800 --> 28:32.730
we just let it go?

28:33.720 --> 28:34.440
No.

28:35.000 --> 28:36.660
They are still waiting for me.

28:36.840 --> 28:37.480
Xinrui.

28:38.000 --> 28:38.400
Can you

28:38.400 --> 28:39.800
call Yuanbao for me

28:40.280 --> 28:42.080
and explain my situation to her?

28:42.680 --> 28:45.720
But I don't have our classmates' contact info,

28:45.840 --> 28:47.770
and Uncle confiscated your phone.

28:47.920 --> 28:49.780
How am I supposed to contact them?

28:50.440 --> 28:51.840
Then can you go see her?

28:52.520 --> 28:54.280
Explain my situation to her.

28:55.040 --> 28:55.840
Okay?

29:01.560 --> 29:02.160
Xinrui.

29:03.240 --> 29:03.920
Okay.

29:05.040 --> 29:07.320
I'll go explain it for you.

29:17.320 --> 29:19.080
You insolent monkey.

29:19.640 --> 29:22.200
To marry the Bull Demon King's sister,

29:22.400 --> 29:25.440
you actually offered your master Tang Sanzang as a wedding gift.

29:25.440 --> 29:28.440
You even invited demons and monsters to eat his flesh.

29:28.560 --> 29:30.320
Do you admit your mistake?

29:30.440 --> 29:33.440
You crazy woman! You've chased me for three days and three nights.

29:33.440 --> 29:36.040
If you weren't a woman, I would have killed you.

29:36.080 --> 29:37.610
You think I'm afraid of you?

29:50.240 --> 29:51.640
Wukong,

29:51.720 --> 29:53.560
how many times have I told you?

29:53.720 --> 29:56.120
Don't throw things around.

29:56.320 --> 29:58.880
What if it hits a kid?

29:59.040 --> 30:00.680
Even if it doesn't hit a kid,

30:00.720 --> 30:02.180
it could hit some flowers.

30:02.880 --> 30:04.680
You seem to have hit me too early.

30:06.280 --> 30:07.280
What should we do?

30:07.520 --> 30:09.050
Never mind. I'll just fall.

30:10.120 --> 30:11.160
It hurts.

30:11.520 --> 30:12.480
Help me up.

30:22.920 --> 30:23.600
Hurry up.

30:25.720 --> 30:26.600
It's starting.

30:28.080 --> 30:30.360
Today is the wedding day of my brother

30:30.400 --> 30:33.040
and my sister Xiangxiang.

30:33.520 --> 30:34.520
Next, I announce

30:34.800 --> 30:38.800
that I will also marry Fairy Zixia.

30:40.320 --> 30:41.250
What did you say?

30:42.160 --> 30:44.090
You are going to marry Fairy Zixia?

30:44.320 --> 30:45.160
My wife.

30:46.720 --> 30:49.320
Are you planning to keep a mistress?

30:49.400 --> 30:50.880
How could I, my wife?

30:51.040 --> 30:52.800
It's a rumor.

30:53.440 --> 30:54.720
Like hell I'll believe you.

30:54.720 --> 30:55.600
Take this.

30:56.760 --> 30:58.720
I'm sorry, my wife.

31:00.280 --> 31:01.680
Still can't get through?

31:03.360 --> 31:04.290
What should I do?

31:11.040 --> 31:11.680
Come on.

31:12.160 --> 31:13.200
Come on, Xiong.

31:13.320 --> 31:15.240
Come on, Yuanbao.

31:30.280 --> 31:32.760
Joker, you bastard.

31:33.040 --> 31:34.080
Come out here!

31:46.800 --> 31:47.440
Yuanbao.

31:48.080 --> 31:49.000
Keep acting.

31:49.080 --> 31:49.960
Keep acting.

31:50.040 --> 31:50.760
Come on.

31:50.960 --> 31:52.000
I am here.
